  "description": "<p>PLEASE CALL 65666-156 FOR INTERVIEW</p><p>Location: Joo Koon MRT (3 bus stops, 15 minutes from Joo Koon MRT)</p><p>Working hours: 8am to 12pm Monday to Friday, NO working on weekends and Public Holidays</p><p>Start-Work timing is negotiable</p><p>Salary: Monthly $1000 + Transport Allowance $100</p><p>Benefits: CPF, Annual Bonus, Annual Leave, Medical Leave, Hospitalisation Leave</p><p>Job Scope:</p><p>Need to climb one flight of stairs</p><p>1) Wash 2 toilets (1 male, 1 female)</p><p>2) Wiping desks and office furniture e.g. cabinet tops, office equipment etc</p><p>3) Vacuuming, Sweeping and Mopping floor</p><p>4) Maintain cleanliness of small pantry</p><p>5) Clear trash</p>",
